name: Vighnaharta
description: There are various religious beliefs of each and everyone, for me it's ganapati bappa. whatever i am or i will be because of my faith and trust on the bappa! he's called vighnaharta(the obstacle remover) and there are various beliefs for that feels almost like a miracle. This piece was made with all of my heart and worships towards the ganapati bappa. Super happy and excited to mint this and share my experience and beliefs towards ganapati bappa! hope y'all like it.
